query:
INSERT INTO song(
            song_path,
            modified_date,
            created_date,
            last_scanned_date,
            artist_id,
            song_title,
            album_id,
            track_number,
            disc_number,
            song_year,
            song_month,
            song_day,
            duration,
            sample_rate,
            bit_rate,
            file_size,
            album_art_path,
            fingerprint
            )
            values
            (
                ?, ?, ?, ?,
                (SELECT artist_id FROM artist WHERE artist_name = ?), 
                ?, 
                (
                    SELECT album_id FROM album al
                    INNER JOIN artist ar ON ar.artist_id = al.artist_id
                    WHERE al.album_name = ? AND ar.artist_name = ?
                ), 
                ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?
            )
            ON CONFLICT(song_path) DO UPDATE
            SET last_scanned_date = ?;
